<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2249] ParallelMultiSearcher should shut down thread pool on close</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2249</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;ParallelMultiSearcher does not shut down its internal thread pool on close. As a result, programs that create multiple instances of this class over their lifetime end up &quot;leaking&quot; threads.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12455352">LUCENE-2249</key>
            <summary>ParallelMultiSearcher should shut down thread pool on close</summary>
